    {
      "id": "93",
      "name": "Media",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Teaser dan Trailer",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 1,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "Teaser Kisah: Cita Rasa Dunia",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/24/237301566/1062f1cb3cf7147dc48b249b75c30c10_6187059567318529523.png"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "YouTube:",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "2 Oktober 2021",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Waktu yang berlalu ditandai dengan makanan dan minuman yang kita nikmati sambil bersenang-senang — yang didapatkan dari anugerah alam. Dari dulu hingga sekarang, tahun demi tahun berlalu dalam sekejap mata.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Asap dari tungku dapur membawa kebahagiaan dan sukacita, kesederhanaan rumah tangga mewarnai kehidupan siang dan malam. Awan halus tak hentinya mengejar bulan, sedangkan perahu dunia tak hentinya mengarungi aliran waktu.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "Teaser Kisah: Kemurkaan Adeptus",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/24/237301566/a027357bf768696f88d82f5d1c6c589f_4635953340932404874.png"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "YouTube:",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "6 Januari 2022",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Kisah ajaib tentang dunia Adeptus, semuanya tidak lagi seperti dulu, kecuali ribuan utas kesedihan yang tersisa.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Nyanyian para pahlawan dikumandangkan, barisan cerita baru ditambahkan, agar cahaya lentera di setiap rumah kembali bersinar terang.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "Animasi Adegan Event “Sekilas Rona di Angkasa: Saat Warna-Warna Mengalir”",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/24/237301566/5fc72b4328567c8785efb5907e0ad078_7739075259872961470.png"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "YouTube:",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "31 Januari 2022",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Nyala kembang api memenuhi angkasa bagai bintang yang bersinar untuk menyambut masa kemakmuran.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Warnanya yang indah membawa harapan dari semua orang. Dalam cahayanya yang menyilaukan, semoga gunung dan bulan bisa tetap mempertahankan keindahan abadi mereka.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "Adegan Animasi \"Dentang Lonceng di Malam yang Indah\": Perayaan Cahaya",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/24/237301566/f549ae83e69ae6253ebc1b46bb599873_529651397798615907.png"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "YouTube:",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "21 Januari 2023",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Tahun yang baru membawa harapan baru, teman terdekat, dan juga keberuntungan.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Di malam yang penuh warna ini, Pelabuhan Liyue tidak hanya dipenuhi Lentera Xiao, tetapi juga musik-musik yang mengalunkan melodi terindahnya.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "Teaser Kisah: Gema Suara di Hati",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/24/237301566/083477d4fe3e4626f8d54ba962d5cae2_2363857075314921546.png"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "YouTube:",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "21 Januari 2023",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Seperti kepulan asap yang menghilang dalam sekejap mata, seperti tangkai yang mengambang tanpa akar.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Aliran air mengalir, menyapu butiran debu yang ada.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "Video Pendek Kumpulan Pemandangan Genshin Impact: Liyue",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/24/237301566/50e9716fc5f9012a00e38edd53ac83e2_3420861946456836153.png"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "YouTube:",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "21 Juni 2023",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Pemandangan pegunungan yang menjulang dan bebatuan raksasa. Menakjubkan dan tak tergoyahkan.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Pelabuhan komersial penuh hiruk-pikuk yang telah menyambut ribuan kapal.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
